<item>
            <title>[PIG-3958] TestMRJobStats is broken in 0.13 and trunk</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3958</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a regression of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3913&quot; title=&quot;Pig should use job&amp;#39;s jobClient wherever possible (fixes local mode counters)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3913&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3913&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. It changed some method signature, and that breaks the unit test.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
